Author: mud_octopus
Text: You absolutely can tell someone that, and you really should if you skip anymore insulin. You know how dangerous this is. You know the risks, so I'm not going to remind you of them, but really, please take care of yourself and ask for help if you can't get this under control. <3

Author: radicalcantaloop
Text: I’m going to get ketone test strips tomorrow just to double check that I’m not in ketoacidosis (if I am then that is Very Very Bad). Hopefully those results will be good. I don’t even know what I’ll do if they aren’t. I can’t exactly tell anyone that I’ve been refusing to take my meds because I’m afraid of getting fatter y’know
